                    (b) if the participation record was prepared by the home educator parent of the child, that parent is to provide a copy of it to the Secretary –
            as soon as reasonably practicable after the commencement day.
            (3) If immediately before the commencement day a child was exempt or excused under the Youth Participation in Education and Training (Guaranteeing Futures) Act 2005 from participating in an eligible option within the meaning of that Act, the child is exempt from participating in an approved learning program.
